//
main
-users
  -new user
    -make a unique uid
    -encrypt password
    -set all values to 0

  -no users
    -make an admin please
  -admin
  -non admin

  -admin
    -user
      -games
      -stats
    -add user
      -update games_stats file
      -update user_data file
    -edit user
    -delete user

-games
  -hangman
    -read word dict
      choose a word
    -play game
      6 chances
      -letters
        check if input is anywhere in the word
      -words
        check if input is the same as the word

  -math quiz
    -difficulty
      easy
        two value
      medium
        three
      hard
        five

    -multiply, divide, subtract, add
    -check if input is the same

  -tic-tac-toe
    -arr[3][3]
      012
      345
      678
    -check system
      -check horizontal
        012, 345, 678
      -check vertical
        036, 147, 258
      -check diagonal
        048, 246

    -computer
      -ai will randomly cycle through possible wins, defined above

